description:
ExternalGeranCell: Metadata and configuration data for external GERAN cells in a radio access network.

- dateTime: Timestamp of data record creation.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographical area where the cell is located.
- CellId: Unique identifier for the cell (likely combining site and cell).
- Id2: Redundant/alternative cell identifier.
- Id3: Ancillary identifier (purpose unclear).
- Id4: Alternative cell identifier, potentially structured.
- vsDataType: Data type identifier.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of data format.
- ExternalGeranCell.userLabel: User-defined label for the cell (currently empty).
- ExternalGeranCell.bcc: Base station color code.
- ExternalGeranCell.zzzTemporary12: Placeholder column (meaning unclear).
- ExternalGeranCell.zzzTemporary11: Placeholder column (meaning unclear).
- ExternalGeranCell.zzzTemporary10: Placeholder column (meaning unclear).
- ExternalGeranCell.zzzTemporary8: Placeholder column (meaning unclear).
- ExternalGeranCell.cellIdentity: Unique cell identifier within the location area.
- ExternalGeranCell.zzzTemporary9: Placeholder column (meaning unclear).
- ExternalGeranCell.dtmSupport: DTM (Dual Transfer Mode) support status.
- ExternalGeranCell.lac: Location Area Code.
- ExternalGeranCell.ncc: Numbering Class Code.
- ExternalGeranCell.masterGeranCellId: ID of the master GERAN cell (currently empty).
- ExternalGeranCell.geranFrequencyRef: Reference to GERAN frequency configuration.
- ExternalGeranCell.isRemoveAllowed: Boolean indicating if cell removal is allowed.
- ExternalGeranCell.rac: Routing Area Code.
- ExternalGeranCell.plmnIdentity: PLMN (Public Land Mobile Network) Identity (currently empty).
- ExternalGeranCell.externalGeranCellId: External unique identifier for the GERAN cell.
- ExternalGeranCell.rimAssociationStatus: RIM (Radio Interface Module) association status.
- ExternalGeranCell.timeOfCreation: Timestamp of cell creation.
- ExternalGeranCell.timeOfLastModification: Timestamp of last modification (currently empty).
- ExternalGeranCell.zzzTemporary1: Placeholder column (meaning unclear).
- ExternalGeranCell.zzzTemporary2: Placeholder column (meaning unclear).
- ExternalGeranCell.rimCapable: RIM capability status.
- ExternalGeranCell.zzzTemporary3: Placeholder column (meaning unclear).
- ExternalGeranCell.zzzTemporary4: Placeholder column (meaning unclear).
- ExternalGeranCell.zzzTemporary5: Placeholder column (meaning unclear).
- ExternalGeranCell.lastModification: Last modification status.
- ExternalGeranCell.reservedBy: Reference to entity that reserved this cell (likely for coordination with other network elements).
